Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.util

Provides general purpose, helper classes used internally by CloudSim Plus.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    WorkloadModel
    Provides methods to be implemented by classes that generate a list of (Cloudlets) (jobs) to be submitted to a DatacenterBroker for execution inside some VMs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Conversion
    A class that provides a set of methods for unit conversion.
    DataCloudTags
    Contains additional tags for the DataCloud functionalities, such as file information retrieval, file transfers, and storage info.
    ExecutionTimeMeasurer
    Measurement of execution times of CloudSim's methods.
    Log
    Logger used for performing logging of the simulation process.
    MathUtil
    A class containing multiple convenient math functions.
    ResourceLoader
    Loads a resource file/directory that is contained inside the directory of a given class.
    WorkloadFileReader
    This class is responsible for reading resource traces from a file and creating a list of (Cloudlets) (jobs).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Log.Level
    An enum that may be used to define the level (type) of a log message.

Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.util Description

Provides general purpose, helper classes used internally by CloudSim Plus.
